						<div class="postbody">I was referring to the price of the game board when new. In the case of a console, the &quot;machine&quot; would be the user's existing TV along with the set of composite video encoder and joypad decoder that commonly goes by &quot;SuperGun&quot;.<br /><br />As for Atlantis: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://nintendoeverything.com/a-look-into-nintendos-unreleased-game-boy-successor/">https://nintendoeverything.com/a-look-i ... successor/</a><!-- m --></div>

